<p>
	<h3>
		Polaroid Snap by &nbsp;Polaroid&nbsp;
	</h3>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	Polaroid（宝丽来）公司在近日的 IFA 大会上推出了最新产品 Polaroid Snap。不仅继承了即时成像的功能，还采用 ZINK 零油墨打印技术，无需墨盒、调色剂就能打印出高品质的全彩的标准 6 英寸照片。从按下快门到打出照片不到一分钟，并能轻松传到电子设备上。而 ZINK 相纸的底层涂有粘合剂，可以直接将照片贴在墙上。另外，这款相机也是 Polaroid 推出的型号最小的一款，能直接放在口袋里。有黑、白、红、蓝四种颜色，预计今年年底出售，售价 99 美元。<a href="http://www.polaroid.com/news/polaroid-snap-instant-digital-camera-share-the-fun-with-one-snap-one-print" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/e72ed7ab496c.jpg" width="1080" height="699" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/ce91ad1f7c43.jpg" width="1080" height="699" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/779c4d407154.jpg" width="1080" height="699" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/970142c20287.jpg" width="1080" height="699" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/9a0e2792af8a.jpg" width="1080" height="699" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<h3>
		“armure”手包 by odo fioravanti
	</h3>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	专门制作 3D 打印饰品的品牌 maison 203，邀请意大利的设计团队 odo fioravanti 设计了一款松果瓣手包。外表不规则的圆瓣就是模拟了松球的形状，巧妙地排列成对称的效果，具有立体的质感。手包由烧结尼龙材质制作，包内藏有磁扣，方便打开。目前正在巴黎家居装饰博览会展出，之后会上线出售。<span><a href="http://www.maison203.com/#" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/7496c30278cd.jpg" width="818" height="546" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/41f5bdbe12cd.jpg" width="818" height="546" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/e4a7c774b44c.jpg" width="818" height="546" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/26b8c056d58e.jpg" width="818" height="863" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/9ed76d015235.jpg" width="818" height="1227" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<h3>
		&nbsp;FLAT-PACKED CHAIR by Etc.etc.
	</h3>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	用 6 根相同的木棍和一块木板做一把椅子看似简单，但想要获得舒服感受就得找好角度。来自丹麦的设计组合“ etc.etc. ”就为立陶宛的家具品牌 emko 做了这样一组椅子，呈现出一种微妙的美感。它可以套上一块布做靠背，也可以组合成不同的颜色，即便是 4 岁的小孩，也可以参与组装并在上面画画。这把椅子可能是世界上能放进最小盒子去快递的椅子了，但最重要的是，它有一颗游戏心。&nbsp;<a href="http://www.etcetc-studio.com/#/naive/" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/008c9e8e26b9.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/3283bead7775.jpg" width="750" height="501" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/632834f222ef.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/985eb7f42fdf.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/ec471f18069c.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/52e8ad705ccd.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/368043ba1ec0.jpg" width="600" height="400" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<h3>
		Spangle by Park Chan-ju
	</h3>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	这款无线音频的灵感来自在音乐课上常玩的打击乐器三角架，声音清脆响亮，当它接收到手机的指令时，就可以最大化地放出声音。它同时也兼具三角形的稳定性，简洁好看。但对于无线音频来说，尽可能放大声音就是最大的价值。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/a8bb450c7c65.jpg" width="1050" height="735" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/4318dc767695.jpg" width="1050" height="837" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/59a5e6bbac05.jpg" width="1050" height="722" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/b50637fca700.jpg" width="1050" height="636" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/fdeeb5e2c230.jpg" width="1050" height="706" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<h3>
		香料植物清洁刷 by alessandra baldereschi
	</h3>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	米兰的设计师 alessandra baldereschi 用香料植物做了一套家用清洁刷，植物夹在两块橡胶做的薄片中间，除了充当清洁的刷子，还可以发挥这些植物的特性，比如装上薄荷或者甘菊都有防蚊虫的功效，而迷迭香可以抗菌，薰衣草除了除臭外也能防腐。他还另外用硬纸板做了 17 种不同形状和颜色的“袋子”，用图形来标注植物的功用，可谓脑洞奇大。<a href="http://www.designboom.com/design/alessandra-baldereschi-grandmother-tips-aromatic-tools-09-04-2015/" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/9503d3d0ebb5.jpg" width="818" height="480" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/9f71d0321f1e.jpg" width="950" height="849" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="http://cms.qdaily.com/uploads/image/201509/8e085787ffa4.jpg" width="818" height="595" title=" " alt=" " style="text-align:center;" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/d6fe206c7c21.jpg" width="950" height="672" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201509/6c3cd02508b6.jpg" width="818" height="474" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
